  <br>
  <span style="color:#1e3060">── SYMBOLS ─────</span><br>
  ♚ King &nbsp; ♛ Queen<br>
  ♜ Rook &nbsp; ♝ Bishop<br>
  ♞ Knight ♟ Pawn
</div>

<div id="keys">
  ↑↓←→ strafe · Z/X up/down · drag rotate · scroll zoom<br>
  R=orbit · T/Y/U zoom levels · click piece (human turn)<br>
